Note that $\mathbf{p}$ is a scalar multiple of $\mathbf{w},$ say $\mathbf{p} = c \mathbf{w}.$  Then
\[\|\mathbf{p}\| = |c| \|\mathbf{w}\|,\]so $\frac{\|\mathbf{p}\|}{\|\mathbf{v}\|} = \frac{|c| \|\mathbf{w}\|}{\|\mathbf{v}\|}.$  Also,
\[\|\mathbf{v}\|^2 = \|\mathbf{p}\|^2 + \|\mathbf{v} - \mathbf{p}\|^2 = \|c \mathbf{w}\|^2 + \|\mathbf{v} - c \mathbf{w}\|^2.\]Since $\mathbf{w}$ is orthogonal to $\mathbf{v} - c \mathbf{w},$
\[\|\mathbf{v} - c \mathbf{w}\|^2 = \|\mathbf{v}\|^2 - c^2 \|\mathbf{w}\|^2.\]Hence,
\[\|\mathbf{v}\|^2 = c^2 \|\mathbf{w}\|^2 + \|\mathbf{v}\|^2 - c^2 \|\mathbf{w}\|^2,\]so $c^2 = \frac{\|\mathbf{p}\|^2}{\|\mathbf{w}\|^2} = \frac{\|\mathbf{p}\|}{\|\mathbf{v}\|} \cdot \frac{\|\mathbf{v}\|}{\|\mathbf{w}\|} = \frac{25}{49}.$  Since $c$ is nonnegative,
\[c = \frac{5}{7}.\]Then
\[\|\mathbf{q}\| = \|\mathbf{p}\| \cdot \frac{|\mathbf{v} \cdot \mathbf{p}|}{\|\mathbf{p}\| \|\mathbf{v}\|} = \frac{5}{7} \|\mathbf{w}\| \cdot \frac{|\mathbf{v} \cdot \mathbf{w}|}{\|\mathbf{v}\| \|\mathbf{w}\|} = \frac{5}{7} \cdot \frac{|\mathbf{v} \cdot \mathbf{w}|}{\|\mathbf{v}\|}.\]Thus,
\[\frac{\|\mathbf{q}\|}{\|\mathbf{v}\|} = \boxed{\frac{5}{7}}.\]

